1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,050
[Episode 46]
[Motel, Bangkok]

2
00:00:17,770 --> 00:00:21,150
Your boyfriend told me
you like this style

3
00:00:31,090 --> 00:00:35,090
Too bad
your boyfriend didn't join us

4
00:00:36,750 --> 00:00:37,950
I was mentally prepared

5
00:00:37,950 --> 00:00:41,010
I came specifically to experience
this group activity

6
00:00:43,470 --> 00:00:45,770
What the hell is Bin up to?

7
00:00:46,390 --> 00:00:48,990
Setting up a meeting at a motel but not coming in

8
00:00:49,590 --> 00:00:52,890
Leaving me alone
with this cosplay girl

9
00:00:53,810 --> 00:00:55,210
I can't take this anymore

10
00:00:56,790 --> 00:01:00,670
Maybe it's for the best
I'm not very good at that sort of thing anyway

11
00:01:03,240 --> 00:01:08,210
Your voice is trembling
Are you cold or excited?

12
00:01:09,550 --> 00:01:14,380
Damn, is this really
what I've been watching all along?

13
00:01:15,090 --> 00:01:18,390
It's actually happening
What should I do now?

14
00:01:27,870 --> 00:01:30,110
It's only been five minutes

15
00:01:30,110 --> 00:01:32,690
Why does it feel
like an hour has passed?

16
00:01:33,479 --> 00:01:36,090
Fuzhi used to wait for me
in the car like this for an hour

17
00:01:36,090 --> 00:01:37,840
How did he endure it every time?

18
00:01:37,970 --> 00:01:39,430
Or maybe he didn't even...

19
00:01:45,289 --> 00:01:48,090
[To Be Continued]
